snippet.title: EMERGENCY MEETING: An Among Us Song [by Random Encounters] (feat. Katie Herbert & Kevin Clark)
snippet.description:
Suspicion is building among us... Can the Crewmates out the Impostor, or will this Emergency Meeting become their last? Watch us PLAY AMONG US ➤ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v_51wmTTd5k

GET THE SONG ON ITUNES ➤ https://music.apple.com/us/album/emergency-meeting-among-us-song-feat-katie-herbert/1533462748
SPOTIFY ➤ https://open.spotify.com/track/5XkC7pQUQaEw5H3HL04Sao
GOOGLE PLAY ➤ https://play.google.com/store/music/album/Random_Encounters_Emergency_Meeting_An_Among_Us_So?id=Bpgfky7qskyrb7sgj7gjvoniso4&hl=en_US
AMAZON ➤ https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08K3SW1YM
BLOOPERS ➤ https://youtu.be/mratI5JgBcQ
MAKING AN AMONG US COSTUME ➤ https://youtu.be/7lf3_H-502o
DESTROYING THE SET ➤ https://youtu.be/rn3EHyjeQEQ

Mix, master, and awesome guitars by our incredibly sus friend, FamilyJules ➤ https://www.youtube.com/user/FamilyJules7X

(Did you find The Beard in every musical? Tell us his timecode in the comments!)

✸BECOME AN ENCOUNTERER✸
Hit the Bell and Watch us Weekly!

HELP US MAKE MUSICALS ☞ www.patreon.com/randomencounters
=======================
✪ GET RANDOM ENCOUNTERS GEAR! ✪
RE-EXCLUSIVE:
➥https://shop.bbtv.com/collections/random-encounters
=======================
LYRICS:
Impostors are among us
Like fiendish, furtive fungus!
The chance of death’s humongous!
We must stop them now!

Someone in our midst is a fiendish traitor,
Mimicking the forms of the crew…
Tan saw me assist with the generator-
-that’s not true!

I was watching Red head to Navigations-
-I was getting trash dislodged!
Radios were dead in Communications…
-Certainly sabotage!

This is inviting a conspiracy for sure!
What if the killer’s lurking in our crew?

What are you hiding? Perhaps you’re the saboteur!
I was with Pink! -Something here stinks, and we think that it’s you!

We caught you, you imposter!
You thought that you could foster
Mistrust within our roster-
It can’t save you now!

It’s a little strange, how you rushed to voting…
Turning on our own without proof…
Paranoia’s all that you’ve been promoting-
What if that “imposter” was just telling the truth?

Any bystander will have seen me doing tasks!
I think I saw her crawling down the vent…

This is all slander! The imposter’s been unmasked!
Spare us your lies! Your phony disguise cannot hide your real intent!

We’ve found the true imposter!
Let’s send this double-crosser
Back to her flying saucer!
It won’t save you now!

Red’s been faking fixing all the wires!
No use making me sound like a liar!

How was I so blind to your deceptions?
Pretty strong words for a fake!
You’re the one behind this whole insurrection!
-If I go down, I’m taking you with me!

No matter how you posture,
I know you’re an impostor!
It’s time to kill the monster-
Heaven help me now!

There’s one more still among us…
Deception has undone us.
What has this madness brung us?
Who will save us now?
